Attribution 4.0 International License (CC-BY-4.0).
See https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/ for the full text.

Original paper text & figures (sourced from Open Access publications) retain
their upstream Creative Commons / publisher OA licences. Each trace's
`_provenance.source.license` field records the per-paper license. Users
redistributing derived works are responsible for compliance with the most
restrictive applicable upstream license.
